<h3 id="html-structure"><a href="#html-structure">HTML structure</a></h3>

<section class="prose">
  <dl>
    <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;div&gt;</code></dt>
    <dd>Main container with centered layout utilities:
      <ul>
        <li><code>flex flex-col items-center justify-center</code>: centers content</li>
        <li><code>gap-6</code>: spacing between sections</li>
        <li><code>p-6 md:p-12</code>: responsive padding</li>
        <li><code>text-center text-balance</code>: centered text with better wrapping</li>
      </ul>
      <dl>
        <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;header&gt;</code></dt>
        <dd>Header section containing the icon/avatar, title, and description:
          <ul>
            <li><code>max-w-sm</code>: constrains width for readability</li>
            <li><code>gap-2</code> or <code>gap-3</code>: spacing between elements</li>
          </ul>
          <dl>
            <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;div&gt;</code> <span class="badge-secondary">Optional</span></dt>
            <dd>Media container for icon or avatar:
              <ul>
                <li>For icons: <code>bg-muted text-foreground size-10 rounded-lg</code></li>
                <li>For avatars: <code>size-12 rounded-full grayscale</code></li>
                <li>For avatar groups: <code>flex -space-x-2</code> with ring utilities</li>
              </ul>
            </dd>
            <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;h3&gt;</code></dt>
            <dd>Title with <code>text-lg font-medium tracking-tight</code></dd>
            <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;p&gt;</code></dt>
            <dd>Description with <code>text-muted-foreground text-sm/relaxed</code></dd>
          </dl>
        </dd>
        <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;section&gt;</code> <span class="badge-secondary">Optional</span></dt>
        <dd>Content area for actions (buttons, inputs, etc.):
          <ul>
            <li><code>max-w-sm</code> or <code>max-w-md</code>: constrains width</li>
            <li><code>flex flex-col items-center gap-3</code>: vertical layout with spacing</li>
          </ul>
        </dd>
        <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;a&gt;</code> or other elements <span class="badge-secondary">Optional</span></dt>
        <dd>Additional links or actions outside the main content section</dd>
      </dl>
    </dd>
  </dl>
</section>

